    <div class="content" style="background-color: #f2f2f2">
        <h3>About Cup-of-Sugar</h3>
        <h6>People of all ages often seek out opportunities to support their local communities.  On the flip side, non-profit organizations exist in nearly every town that contribute to community well-being, yet they lack resources to provide their services.
        <br /><br />Cup-of-Sugar intends to help facilitate the coalescing of volunteer "supply" and organizations' need for volunteer service and donations.  This site allows non-profit organizations to list needs for both goods and services.  Users can then browse through these needs in order to determine how they can lend some support.
        <br /><br />Whether you represent a charitable institution that needs a little "sugar" or you're just looking to lend a helping hand, let Cup-of-Sugar aid your journey to bettering your local community.
        <br /><br />&#9825;</h6>
